        "title": "Fraud Detection in Transactions Dataset",
        "subtitle": "1,000 simulated financial transactions for binary classification and anomaly det",
        "description": "**\ud83c\uddec\ud83c\udde7 English:**\n\nThis dataset contains 1,000 synthetic financial transactions designed for fraud detection experiments. Each record includes transaction amount, merchant category, device type, and a binary label indicating whether the transaction is fraudulent. Only 5% of transactions are marked as fraud to reflect a real-world class imbalance.\n\n**Use this dataset to:**\n\n- Train fraud detection models with class imbalance\n- Apply techniques like XGBoost, SMOTE, or Isolation Forest\n- Explore anomaly detection and fraud pattern analysis\n\n---\n\n**\ud83c\uddf9\ud83c\uddf7 T\u00fcrk\u00e7e:**\n\nBu sentetik veri seti, doland\u0131r\u0131c\u0131l\u0131k tespiti \u00e7al\u0131\u015fmalar\u0131na uygun olacak \u015fekilde olu\u015fturulmu\u015ftur. Toplamda 1.000 i\u015flem bilgisi i\u00e7erir ve her i\u015flem, tutar, sat\u0131c\u0131 t\u00fcr\u00fc, cihaz t\u00fcr\u00fc gibi alanlarla birlikte gelir. Yaln\u0131zca %5 oran\u0131nda i\u015flem doland\u0131r\u0131c\u0131l\u0131k olarak i\u015faretlenmi\u015ftir.\n\n**Bu veri setiyle:**\n\n- Dengesiz veri k\u00fcmelerinde s\u0131n\u0131fland\u0131rma yap\u0131labilir\n- SMOTE, XGBoost, Isolation Forest gibi algoritmalar uygulanabilir\n- Anomali tespiti ve sahtekarl\u0131k analizleri ger\u00e7ekle\u015ftirilebilir\n\n\n\n=== About this file ===\n\nAbout this file\nThis file includes 1,000 synthetic transactions, including 5% fraudulent cases. Created to simulate real-world fraud detection scenarios using machine learning.\n\n\n=== Columns & descriptions ===\n\ntransaction_id: Unique identifier for each transaction\namount: Transaction amount in USD\nmerchant_type: Type of merchant (e.g., groceries, travel)\ndevice_type: Device used for the transaction\nlabel: 1 = Fraudulent, 0 = Normal\n",
